  <summary>A fast, cross-platform, OpenGL terminal emulator</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Velacritty is a GPU-accelerated terminal emulator with sensible defaults that allows for extensive configuration.
      By integrating with other applications rather than reimplementing their functionality, it manages to provide
      a flexible set of features with high performance.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Wayland native</li>
      <li>X11 native</li>
      <li>DE agnostic</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

